569
00:29:20,310 --> 00:29:22,230
Rest assured. I won't lose.

570
00:29:25,270 --> 00:29:26,270
Come on.

571
00:29:26,510 --> 00:29:27,510
Here.

572
00:29:31,190 --> 00:29:32,400
What a bad luck.

573
00:29:34,260 --> 00:29:35,260
Zhang Long.

574
00:29:47,110 --> 00:29:48,110
Thank you.

575
00:30:04,270 --> 00:30:05,270
Sako,

576
00:30:07,190 --> 00:30:08,520
here's a letter for you.

577
00:30:13,110 --> 00:30:14,770
I wrote it for you especially.

578
00:30:16,480 --> 00:30:20,500
(To Sachiko)

579
00:30:34,600 --> 00:30:36,260
(To Jiang Xinhong)

580
00:30:52,990 --> 00:30:54,070
What is it?

581
00:30:54,550 --> 00:30:55,790
A love letter!

582
00:30:57,870 --> 00:30:59,190
Shameless!

583
00:30:59,350 --> 00:31:02,110
Hey, when will you tell her the truth?

584
00:31:02,310 --> 00:31:03,550
I can't wait.

585
00:31:06,610 --> 00:31:08,360
Aren't we going on a spring outing in a few days?

586
00:31:08,360 --> 00:31:10,690
Let's wait for the day of the spring outing

587
00:31:10,690 --> 00:31:12,020
to make fun of her.

588
00:31:17,590 --> 00:31:18,790
Don't come over here!

589
00:31:18,910 --> 00:31:20,570
I don't want to sit next to you.

590
00:31:20,590 --> 00:31:21,950
There's a bad smell on you.

591
00:31:21,950 --> 00:31:22,990
It stinks.

592
00:31:23,300 --> 00:31:24,350
Is she gonna join us? Then I don't wanna be in this photo.

593
00:31:24,350 --> 00:31:25,550
Is she gonna join us? Then I don't wanna be in this photo.

594
00:31:25,550 --> 00:31:26,550
Nor do I.

595
00:31:26,750 --> 00:31:28,810
We don't wanna be in the photo either.

596
00:31:29,270 --> 00:31:31,750
Mr. Liu, do something! Do you wanna take a photo of us or not?

597
00:31:31,750 --> 00:31:33,350
How are we supposed to take a group photo with her around?

598
00:31:33,350 --> 00:31:34,990
We all don't want to be next to you. Just go.

599
00:31:34,990 --> 00:31:37,250
We can't take this photo with you around.

600
00:31:37,510 --> 00:31:38,510
How disgusting!

601
00:31:42,910 --> 00:31:45,430
Guys, come back here for the group photo.

602
00:31:46,190 --> 00:31:47,110
Okay.

603
00:31:47,110 --> 00:31:48,230
Look at me!

604
00:31:48,630 --> 00:31:50,910
Three, two, one.

605
00:31:52,950 --> 00:31:55,430
Okay. Go have fun, guys!

606
00:31:55,630 --> 00:31:57,110
But don't go anywhere dangerous.

607
00:31:57,110 --> 00:31:57,910
Mind your own safety.

608
00:31:57,910 --> 00:31:59,990
Okay, sir.

609
00:32:00,990 --> 00:32:02,110
Did she go that way?

610
00:32:02,750 --> 00:32:03,750
Let's go.

611
00:32:16,150 --> 00:32:17,790
Why don't we play a game?

612
00:32:19,230 --> 00:32:20,230
(To Jiang Xinhong)

613
00:32:20,910 --> 00:32:23,030
Sachiko wrote this love letter to me.

614
00:32:23,790 --> 00:32:24,910
Give it back to me!

615
00:32:25,230 --> 00:32:26,350
Jiang Xinhong!

616
00:32:26,390 --> 00:32:27,350
Don't move!

617
00:32:27,350 --> 00:32:29,230
Give it back to me!

618
00:32:30,590 --> 00:32:31,190
Let go of me!

619
00:32:31,190 --> 00:32:32,470
"Dear Xinhong,

620
00:32:33,230 --> 00:32:34,960
when you read this letter, it's like we've met up again."

621
00:32:34,960 --> 00:32:37,070
- Stop reading it! - "During this period of time at school..."

622
00:32:37,070 --> 00:32:42,230
- Let go of me! - "I'm very pleased about our talks on literature."

623
00:32:42,630 --> 00:32:43,550
I beg you!

624
00:32:43,580 --> 00:32:45,830
"The first time I saw you,

625
00:32:46,150 --> 00:32:49,190
I was already attracted to you."

626
00:32:49,630 --> 00:32:50,350
Let me go!

627
00:32:50,510 --> 00:32:51,840
"Every time I wrote..."

628
00:32:52,350 --> 00:32:53,350
Screw you!

629
00:32:53,750 --> 00:32:55,190
Acting all hoity-toity, huh?

630
00:32:55,190 --> 00:32:56,650
Come on. Give me the water.

631
00:33:03,140 --> 00:33:04,350
You stinky fish seller!

632
00:33:04,350 --> 00:33:05,350
Bah!

633
00:33:06,310 --> 00:33:07,310
Let's go!

634
00:33:08,350 --> 00:33:10,070
The next day, we heard the news

635
00:33:10,110 --> 00:33:12,240
about Sachiko dying in a car accident.

636
00:33:12,630 --> 00:33:14,020
No one felt sad.

637
00:33:14,710 --> 00:33:17,110
Instead, they found it quite interesting.

638
00:33:17,200 --> 00:33:19,270
Jiang Xinhong even wrote a song in particular

639
00:33:19,270 --> 00:33:20,530
to make fun of Sachiko.

640
00:33:22,150 --> 00:33:26,830
None of us imagined that those who sang it would die two days later.

641
00:33:28,190 --> 00:33:30,870
At first, we didn't take it seriously.

642
00:33:32,270 --> 00:33:33,390
Some time later,

643
00:33:34,230 --> 00:33:37,490
more deaths continued to happen to those who sang the song.

644
00:33:38,390 --> 00:33:40,390
That's when we started to feel fear.

645
00:33:42,270 --> 00:33:44,270
I then prepared to transfer to another school.

646
00:33:44,270 --> 00:33:46,200
Now I'm about to leave the country.

647
00:33:48,990 --> 00:33:50,400
When rich people are in trouble,

648
00:33:50,400 --> 00:33:52,860
they make their way out in rich people's way.

649
00:33:53,870 --> 00:33:56,230
Jiang Xinhong is a punk!

650
00:33:57,150 --> 00:34:00,390
He deserves to die a hundred times!

651
00:34:01,230 --> 00:34:03,630
How dare he pretend to be innocent in front of us?

652
00:34:03,630 --> 00:34:04,910
I'm gonna kill him now!

653
00:34:04,990 --> 00:34:05,990
Hey!

654
00:34:08,030 --> 00:34:10,150
Why are all the classmates dead,

655
00:34:11,110 --> 00:34:12,830
except for you and him?

656
00:34:13,230 --> 00:34:15,030
The mastermind of that whole thing

657
00:34:15,030 --> 00:34:16,150
was Jiang Xinhong!

658
00:34:16,750 --> 00:34:18,590
He should've been the first one to die.

659
00:34:18,590 --> 00:34:20,110
After Sachiko's death,

660
00:34:20,540 --> 00:34:22,750
he and I felt odd about that matter,

661
00:34:23,389 --> 00:34:25,050
so we've never sung that song.

662
00:34:25,480 --> 00:34:26,480
What?

663
00:34:27,190 --> 00:34:28,230
Are you happy now,

664
00:34:29,070 --> 00:34:31,199
because he and you have escaped death?

665
00:34:32,030 --> 00:34:33,830
I've told you everything I know.

666
00:34:34,270 --> 00:34:37,469
How are you gonna help me, maintenance guys?

667
00:34:38,230 --> 00:34:39,830
Are you gonna make Sachiko's ghost disappear?

668
00:34:39,830 --> 00:34:40,889
Maintenance guys?

669
00:34:43,350 --> 00:34:44,350
Don't worry.

670
00:34:45,230 --> 00:34:48,389
Soon, everything will disappear.

671
00:34:50,050 --> 00:34:51,659
(Ying Cai High School)

672
00:34:52,310 --> 00:34:53,230
Don't rush into decisions!

673
00:34:53,230 --> 00:34:54,659
We've gotta take some time to make plans for this matter!

674
00:34:54,659 --> 00:34:56,630
My mind won't be at ease unless I kill Jiang Xinhong!

675
00:34:56,630 --> 00:34:58,490
If you kill him, what am I gonna do?

676
00:35:00,270 --> 00:35:00,950
I...

677
00:35:00,950 --> 00:35:01,950
Meng,

678
00:35:01,990 --> 00:35:04,990
what do you mean by that?

679
00:35:05,030 --> 00:35:06,440
If you kill him,

680
00:35:07,230 --> 00:35:08,590
what will become of the White Deer?

681
00:35:08,590 --> 00:35:09,750
After I marry Baijie,

682
00:35:09,750 --> 00:35:11,430
I'll work for the Obsidian with her.

683
00:35:11,430 --> 00:35:13,560
The White Deer will have to rely on you.

684
00:35:13,670 --> 00:35:14,390
Meng,

685
00:35:14,470 --> 00:35:15,630
what's wrong with you?

686
00:35:15,630 --> 00:35:16,670
Baijie is actually a...

687
00:35:16,670 --> 00:35:17,930
What is it with Baijie?

688
00:35:20,990 --> 00:35:22,720
Just stop quarreling. Stop it.

689
00:35:23,310 --> 00:35:25,630
Our priority now is to find the key.

690
00:35:25,950 --> 00:35:27,710
Judging from the current situation, finding the key

691
00:35:27,710 --> 00:35:29,630
means calming the anger in Sako's heart, right?

692
00:35:29,760 --> 00:35:31,550
That is to say, we still need to kill Jiang Xinhong.

693
00:35:31,550 --> 00:35:32,680
Exactly what I want!

694
00:35:34,310 --> 00:35:34,910
Excuse me.

695
00:35:34,990 --> 00:35:36,280
Where is Jiang Xinhong?

696
00:35:36,280 --> 00:35:37,280
He went home.

697
00:35:37,990 --> 00:35:38,630
He went home?

698
00:35:38,630 --> 00:35:39,630
When did he leave?

699
00:35:40,070 --> 00:35:41,830
After he came back from outside at noon,

700
00:35:41,830 --> 00:35:44,230
he packed his stuff and went home in a hurry.

701
00:35:45,630 --> 00:35:46,630
Thank you.

702
00:35:50,630 --> 00:35:51,830
Get your hands off me!

703
00:36:01,350 --> 00:36:02,350
Now this is great.

704
00:36:03,310 --> 00:36:04,950
The key figures are all away.

705
00:36:05,550 --> 00:36:07,430
How are we supposed to find the key?

706
00:36:07,430 --> 00:36:09,890
Shall we ask Mr. Liu to tell them to come back?

707
00:36:09,910 --> 00:36:11,910
Do you think they will show up again?

708
00:36:12,150 --> 00:36:13,830
If not, they'll just be waiting for their deaths at home.

709
00:36:13,830 --> 00:36:14,830
Anyway, Sachiko

710
00:36:14,830 --> 00:36:16,360
is looking for them, not us.

711
00:36:17,670 --> 00:36:19,270
The time left for us

712
00:36:19,430 --> 00:36:20,890
is becoming less and less.

713
00:36:21,220 --> 00:36:22,750
These kids...

714
00:36:23,310 --> 00:36:24,580
What lousy children!

715
00:36:25,440 --> 00:36:27,760
Why must they hurt a little girl like that?

716
00:36:27,760 --> 00:36:30,560
Isn't it just what all wealthy and spoiled kids do?

717
00:36:30,950 --> 00:36:32,390
How boring!

718
00:36:34,270 --> 00:36:35,600
I wish Baijie were here.

719
00:36:35,990 --> 00:36:37,910
She must be a kindhearted person.

720
00:36:38,950 --> 00:36:40,080
How is she doing now?

721
00:36:41,000 --> 00:36:43,260
Even if Baijie is in this door challenge,

722
00:36:43,510 --> 00:36:45,040
she won't talk to you at all.

723
00:36:45,710 --> 00:36:48,030
By the way, now,

724
00:36:48,230 --> 00:36:50,490
she's working along well with Lingling.

725
00:36:50,510 --> 00:36:51,950
They help each other in the door challenges.

726
00:36:51,950 --> 00:36:53,430
They even share one bed at night.

727
00:36:53,430 --> 00:36:54,430
What did you say?

728
00:36:56,630 --> 00:36:58,710
Are you sleeping in the same bed with her?

729
00:36:58,710 --> 00:36:59,390
No. No.

730
00:36:59,430 --> 00:37:00,710
We sleep in separate rooms.

731
00:37:00,710 --> 00:37:01,710
Really?

732
00:37:02,110 --> 00:37:03,510
But Baijie has told me

733
00:37:03,830 --> 00:37:05,950
that the bed is so small

734
00:37:06,070 --> 00:37:09,130
that she and you have to cuddle together when you sleep.

735
00:37:11,350 --> 00:37:12,830
You look like an upright gentleman.

736
00:37:12,830 --> 00:37:16,030
I've never imagined you're actually a brute in disguise!

737
00:37:16,750 --> 00:37:17,750
Xia Rubei,

738
00:37:18,750 --> 00:37:19,460
let's go.

739
00:37:19,710 --> 00:37:20,710
Meng Yu...

740
00:37:22,630 --> 00:37:24,030
Please explain it to him!

741
00:37:24,830 --> 00:37:26,540
Now I'm finding this

742
00:37:26,630 --> 00:37:27,690
very interesting.

743
00:37:27,840 --> 00:37:28,590
Xia Rubei!

744
00:37:28,830 --> 00:37:29,830
Coming!

745
00:37:32,670 --> 00:37:34,540
Why did you have to provoke him?

746
00:37:34,910 --> 00:37:36,190
He said he was bored,

747
00:37:36,270 --> 00:37:37,870
so I spiced things up for him.

748
00:37:38,550 --> 00:37:39,550
Oh, right,

749
00:37:40,350 --> 00:37:42,280
did you say something to Xia Rubei?

750
00:37:42,590 --> 00:37:44,790
Why would she make a funny face at you?

751
00:37:49,070 --> 00:37:50,230
I accidentally

752
00:37:50,670 --> 00:37:52,030
told her the truth.

753
00:37:53,230 --> 00:37:54,430
When did that happen?

754
00:37:55,870 --> 00:37:58,670
When you and Meng Yu went to look for Jiang Xinhong,

755
00:37:58,830 --> 00:38:00,430
she and I both recalled

756
00:38:00,430 --> 00:38:02,230
some troubling issues from childhood.

757
00:38:02,230 --> 00:38:03,630
As we got deeper into our talk,

758
00:38:03,630 --> 00:38:05,290
that secret just slipped out.

759
00:38:06,030 --> 00:38:07,830
Troubling issues in childhood?

760
00:38:09,270 --> 00:38:11,510
Why did you share those with her instead of me?

761
00:38:11,510 --> 00:38:14,830
Well, one thing led to another...

762
00:38:14,830 --> 00:38:16,960
It just felt natural to spill them out.

763
00:38:17,430 --> 00:38:18,430
Okay.

764
00:38:18,480 --> 00:38:19,320
Hey!

765
00:38:19,320 --> 00:38:21,320
Are you upset that I didn't tell you?

766
00:38:21,510 --> 00:38:23,030
I-I still have tons of stories.

767
00:38:23,030 --> 00:38:24,290
I can tell you two more.

768
00:38:30,470 --> 00:38:31,470
Meng Yu,

769
00:38:32,350 --> 00:38:34,350
it's really not what you think it is.

770
00:38:34,630 --> 00:38:37,160
I don't have any ties with Baijie whatsoever.

771
00:39:14,190 --> 00:39:15,190
Zhu Meng,

772
00:39:16,070 --> 00:39:17,070
are you still up?

773
00:39:22,990 --> 00:39:26,470
Sachiko has called herself Sako since she was little.

774
00:39:26,790 --> 00:39:28,470
That's hilarious.
